  m_sTextData "Wolf Hill (named area of interest) is to our southwest. Intelligence suggests there is an operable Mi-24P Hind equipped with 9M114 anti-tank rockets. The Soviets are may attempt to secure this vital piece of equipment and will likely man it if given the opportunity."\
  ""\
  "The mission is simple: Advance to contact and annihilate the enemy. Optional: Either steal the Mi-24P and use it against them or destroy it before or after the Soviets man it themselves (should they attempt to do so)."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
